Path: Nushell
Content:
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6924] updated the 
``nix``
 crate to 
``0.25``
 and removed unused features
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6897] fixed 
``each while``
 behavior when printing and maybe in other situations by fusing the iterator
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6877] wrapped 
``open``
 parse errors from 
``from``
 commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6870] removed unnecessary 
``#[allow(...)]``
 annotations
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6648] reduced required dependencies for diagnostics
paper-lark 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6655] highlighted matching brackets / parentheses
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6923] updated the PR template to mention user-facing changes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6892] improved the error message for 
``get 0``
 on non-collection types
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6867] support ranges in 
``str substring``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6858] fixed 
``ps``
 on Linux
webbedspace 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6919] updated merge to also take single records (closes #5281)
, made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6913] further edits to help messages
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6868] edited a small handful of help messages
kambala-decapitator 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6912] fixed the description of build-string's second example
ChrisDenton 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6824] fixed UNC shares
melMass created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6903] docs: üìù add "map" to each's search terms
zhiburt created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6884] table: Show truncated record differently
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6847] ``table -e``
 Fix stackoverflow (cause endless empty list)
FilipAndersson245 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6865] bumped Windows dependencies
dandavison 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6863] exposed reedline EditCommand::Complete command
nibon7 created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6860] path: fix error message
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6781] Add support to render right prompt on last line of the prompt
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6701] Prepend directory to the binary tarball
Decodetalkers implemented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6791] feat: coredump
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6752] added a more helpful error for calling a decl that exists in a module
